","m":"gentle"},{"d":"तस्याः","m":"his"},{"d":"मुखम्","m":"face"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"रामस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"everything"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"आख्यातुम्","m":"to communicate"},{"d":"उपचक्रमे","m":"started"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"वैदेही कुशलीरामस्सहसुग्रीवलक्ष्मणः ।वभीषणसहायश्चहरीणांसहितोबलैः","trans":"Hanuman said\" O Vaidehi! Sri Rama accompanied by Sugriva and Lakshmana, with the help of Vibheeshana, is doing well.\"","words":[{"d":"वैदेहि","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"सहसुग्रवलक्ष्मणः","m":"and Sugriva, Lakshmana"},{"d":"विभीषणसहायश्च","m":"with the help of Vibheeshana"},{"d":"हरीणाम्","m":"and monkeys"},{"d":"बलैः","m":"army"},{"d":"कुशली","m":"doing well"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"कुशलंचाहसिद्धार्थोहतशत्रुरिमत्रजित् ।विभीषणसहायेनरामेणहरिभिस्सह निहतोरावणोदेविलक्ष्मणेन च वीर्यवान् ।","trans":"\"Noble lady! Sri Rama killed Ravana and won the enemy. He accomplished the purpose with the help of Vibheeshana, the valiant Lakshmana and the monkeys also so to speak. He inquired of your wellbeing.\"","words":[{"d":"अमित्रजित्","m":"won the enemy"},{"d":"हतशत्रुः","m":"killed enemy"},{"d":"सिद्धार्थः","m":"accomplished the purpose"},{"d":"त्वा","m":"your"},{"d":"कुशलम्","m":"wellbeing"},{"d":"चाह","m":"to speak"},{"d":"देवि","m":"noble lady"},{"d":"विभीषणसहायेन","m":"with the help of Vibheeshana"},{"d":"हरिभिः","m":"monkeys also सह also"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणेन","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"valiant"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"निहतः","m":"killed"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"प्रियमाख्यामितेदेविभूयश्चत्वांसभाजये तवप्रभावाद्धर्मजेमहान् रामेणसंयुगे ।लब्धोऽयंविजयस्सीतेस्वस्थाभवगतज्वरा","trans":"\"O noble lady! I am communicating delightful news to you. O Sita, a respectable lady and knowledgeable one, the victory is attained in the combat by the great soul Rama, by virtue of your strength and devotion.\"","words":[{"d":"देवि","m":"noble lady"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"प्रियम्","m":"delightful"},{"d":"आख्यामि","m":"communicated"},{"d":"भूयः","m":"telling"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सभाजये","m":"respectable one"},{"d":"धर्मज्ञे","m":"knower of right knowledge"},{"d":"सीते","m":"Sita"},{"d":"तव","m":"to you"},{"d":"प्रभावात्","m":"strength"},{"d":"संयुगे","m":"in the combat"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"महान्","m":"great self"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"विजयः","m":"victory"},{"d":"लब्दः","m":"attained"},{"d":"गतज्वरा","m":"freed from fear"},{"d":"स्वस्था","m":"strength"},{"d":"भव","m":"your"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"प्रियमाख्यामितेदेविभूयश्चत्वांसभाजये तवप्रभावाद्धर्मजेमहान् रामेणसंयुगे ।लब्धोऽयंविजयस्सीतेस्वस्थाभवगतज्वरा","trans":"\"O noble lady! I am communicating delightful news to you. O Sita, a respectable lady and knowledgeable one, the victory is attained in the combat by the great soul Rama, by virtue of your strength and devotion.\"","words":[{"d":"देवि","m":"noble lady"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"प्रियम्","m":"delightful"},{"d":"आख्यामि","m":"communicated"},{"d":"भूयः","m":"telling"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सभाजये","m":"respectable one"},{"d":"धर्मज्ञे","m":"knower of right knowledge"},{"d":"सीते","m":"Sita"},{"d":"तव","m":"to you"},{"d":"प्रभावात्","m":"strength"},{"d":"संयुगे","m":"in the combat"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"महान्","m":"great self"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"विजयः","m":"victory"},{"d":"लब्दः","m":"attained"},{"d":"गतज्वरा","m":"freed from fear"},{"d":"स्वस्था","m":"strength"},{"d":"भव","m":"your"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"रावणश्चहतश्शत्रुर्लङ्कचैववशीकृता ।मयाह्यलब्न्दिद्रेणधृतेनतवनिर्जये प्रतिज्ञैषाविनिस्तीर्णाबद्ध्वासेतुंमहोदधौ ।","trans":"'Ravana has been killed, Lanka is under our side vanquished completely. Without any sleep, with forbearance, building an extensive bridge on the great ocean, the vow has been redeemed', is Rama's message to you, said Hanuman.","words":[{"d":"शत्रुः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"रावणश्च","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"हतः","m":"killed"},{"d":"लङ्काचैव","m":"in Lanka also"},{"d":"वशीकृता","m":"under control"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"निर्जये","m":"vanquished completely"},{"d":"धृतेन","m":"forbearance"},{"d":"अलब्न्दिद्रेण","m":"without little sleep"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"महोदधौ","m":"on the great ocean"},{"d":"सेतुम्","m":"bridge"},{"d":"बद्ध्वा","m":"constructed"},{"d":"एषा","m":"in that way"},{"d":"प्रतिज्ञा","m":"vow"},{"d":"विनिस्तीर्णा","m":"extensive"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"सम्भ्रमश्च न कर्तव्योवर्तन्त्यारावणालये विभीषणविधेयंहिलङ्कैश्वर्यमिदंकृतम् ।","trans":"\"This Lanka is under Vibheeshana, Lord of Lanka. There is no need for perturbation thinking that you are in Ravana's abode.\"","words":[{"d":"रावणालये","m":"Ravana's abode"},{"d":"वर्तन्त्या","m":"staying"},{"d":"सम्भ्रमः च","m":"perturbation"},{"d":"न कर्तव्यः","m":"not required"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"लङ्कैश्वर्यम्","m":"Lanka's Lord"},{"d":"विभीषणविधेयम्","m":"under Vibheeshana"},{"d":"कृतंहि","m":"has become"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"तदाश्वसिहिविस्रब्धंस्वगृहेपरिवर्तसे अयंचाभ्येतिसम्हृष्टस्त्वद्धर्शनसमुत्सुकः ।","trans":"\"You be at ease, as you are living in your own abode\", said Hanuman consoling Sita. 'Vibheeshana, who is very happy, is eager and favouring to see you.\"","words":[{"d":"तत्","m":"therefore"},{"d":"विस्रब्धम्","m":"be at ease"},{"d":"अश्वसिहि","m":"consoling"},{"d":"स्वगृहे","m":"own house"},{"d":"परिवर्तसे","m":"encompassed"},{"d":"अयंहि","m":"who is"},{"d":"सम्हृष्टः","m":"very happy"},{"d":"त्वद्धर्शनसमुत्सुकः","m":"eager to see you"},{"d":"अभ्येति","m":"favouring"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"एवमुक्तासमुत्पत्यसीताशशिनिभानना प्रहर्षेणावरुद्धासाव्याहर्तुं न शशाक ह ।","trans":"Hanuman having spoken in that way, Sita got up in excessive joy and could not speak naturally.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"that way"},{"d":"उक्ता","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"शशिनिभानना","m":"countenance of moon"},{"d":"समुत्पत्य","m":"got up"},{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"प्रहर्षेण","m":"in joy"},{"d":"अवरुद्धा","m":"stopped"},{"d":"व्याहर्तुम्","m":"to speak"},{"d":"न शशाकह","m":"could not talk naturally."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"ततोऽब्रवीद्धरिवरःसीतामप्रतिजल्पतीम् किंत्वंचिन्तयसेदेविकिं च मांनाभिभाषसे ।","trans":"Then seeing Sita not answering him, the monkey chief asked her\" Why are you not replying. What are you thinking?\"","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"हरिवरः","m":"monkey chief"},{"d":"अप्रतिजल्पतीम्","m":"not replying"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"देवि","m":"Devi"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"किम्","m":"What चिन्तयसे thinking"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"नाभिभाषसे","m":"not answering"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"एवमुक्ताहनुमतासीताधर्मपथेस्थिता अब्रवीत्परमप्रीताबाष्पगद्गदयागिरा ।","trans":"When Hanuman spoke in that way virtuous Sita was overwhelmed with joy and spoke with a voice choked with tears.","words":[{"d":"हनुमता","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्ता","m":"spoken"},{"d":"धर्मपथे","m":"virtuous"},{"d":"स्थिता","m":"stood"},{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"परमप्रीता","m":"very delighted"},{"d":"बाष्पगद्गदया","m":"voice choked with tears"},{"d":"गिरा","m":"speech"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"प्रियमेतदुपश्रुत्यभर्तुर्विजयसंश्रयम् प्रहर्षवशमापन्नानिर्वाक्यास्मिक्षणान्तरम् ।","trans":"\"No doubt that my husband is victorious is very delightful. Hearing this, I am overcome with delight and am unable to speak for a moment.\"","words":[{"d":"भर्तुः","m":"husband"},{"d":"विजयसंश्रयम्","m":"victorious no doubt"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all this"},{"d":"प्रियम्","m":"delighting"},{"d":"उपश्रुत्य","m":"hearing"},{"d":"प्रहर्षवशम्","m":"overcome with delight"},{"d":"आपन्ना","m":"having experienced"},{"d":"क्षणान्तरम्","m":"for a second"},{"d":"निर्वाक्या","m":"not able to speak"},{"d":"अस्मि","m":"I am"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"न हिपश्यामिसदृशंचिन्तयन्तीप्लवङ्गमा मप्रतियाब्यानकस्येहदातुंप्रत्यभिनन्दनम् ।","trans":"\"Hanuman! However, I think to give you a befitting gift for this happy news. I am not able to see any.\"","words":[{"d":"प्लवङ्गम","m":"monkey"},{"d":"चिन्तयन्ती","m":"however I think"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"मप्रतियाख्यानकस्य","m":"to please you"},{"d":"दातुम्","m":"to give"},{"d":"सदृशम्","m":"befitting"},{"d":"प्रत्यभिनन्दनम्","m":"for this happiness"},{"d":"न पश्यामिहि","m":"not able to see"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"नहिपश्यामिततसौम्यपृथिव्यामपिवानर सदृशंयत्प्रियाख्यानेतवदत्त्वाभवेत्सुखम् ।","trans":"\"I am not able to see on this earth, a gift befitting the value of your message, which can be given to you to make you happy.\"","words":[{"d":"प्रियाख्यान","m":"value of your message"},{"d":"सदृशम्","m":"befitting"},{"d":"यत्","m":"such"},{"d":"तव","m":"to you"},{"d":"दत्त्वा","m":"gift"},{"d":"सुखम्","m":"happy"},{"d":"भवेत्","m":"make you"},{"d":"सदृशम्","m":"befitting"},{"d":"किञ्चन","m":"anything"},{"d":"पृथिव्याम्","m":"on this earth"},{"d":"न हिपश्यामि","m":"not able to see"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"हिरण्यंवासुवर्णंवारत्नानिविविधानिच राज्यंवात्रिषुलोकेषुनैतदर्हतिभाषितम् ।","trans":"\"Neither gold or silver or gems, not even kingdom or the three worlds are equal to what you have spoken now.\"","words":[{"d":"हिरण्यंवा","m":"gold or"},{"d":"सुवर्णंवा","m":"silver"},{"d":"विविधानि","m":"several"},{"d":"रत्नानि","m":"gems"},{"d":"त्रिषुलोकेषु","m":"in the three worlds"},{"d":"राज्यंवा","m":"kingdom or"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all this"},{"d":"भाषितम्","m":"spoken now"},{"d":"नार्हति","m":"not equal"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"एवमुक्तस्तुवैदेह्याप्रत्युवाचप्लवङ्गमः प्रगृहीताञ्जलिर्हर्षासतीतायाःप्रमुखेस्थितः ।","trans":"Spoken in that way by Vaidehi, Hanuman stood with folded palms in front of Sita and replied in delight.","words":[{"d":"वैदेह्या","m":"by Vaidehi"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गमाः","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"प्रगृहीताञ्जलिः","m":"in front with palms closed"},{"d":"सीतायाः","m":"Sita"},{"d":"प्रमुखे","m":"chief"},{"d":"स्थितः","m":"stood"},{"d":"हर्षात्","m":"delighted"},{"d":"प्रत्युवाच","m":"replied"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"भर्तुःप्रियहितेयुक्तेभर्तुर्विजयकाङ्क्षिण: स्निग्धमेवंविधंवाक्यंत्वमेवार्हस्यनिन्दिते ।","trans":"\"You alone can speak such affectionate words in this manner wishing victory and welfare of your dear husband. You are irreproachable.\"","words":[{"d":"भर्तुः","m":"husband"},{"d":"प्रियहिते","m":"welfare"},{"d":"युक्ते","m":"such loving"},{"d":"भर्तुः","m":"husband"},{"d":"विजयकाङ्क्षिण:","m":"wishing his victory"},{"d":"अनिन्दिते","m":"irreproachable"},{"d":"स्निग्धम्","m":"loving"},{"d":"एवंविधम्","m":"this manner"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"त्वमेव","m":"you alone"},{"d":"अर्हसि","m":"can speak"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"तवैतद्वचनंसौम्येसारवत् स्निग्धमेव च रत्नौघाद्विविधाच्चापिदेवराज्याद्विशिष्यते ।","trans":"\"O gentle one! Your meaningful words full of affection are more valuable than clusters of gems or Indra, the Lord of gods.\"","words":[{"d":"सौम्ये","m":"gentle"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"सारवत्","m":"meaningful"},{"d":"स्निग्धमेव","m":"full of affection"},{"d":"एतत् वचनम्","m":"such words"},{"d":"विविधात्","m":"many"},{"d":"रत्नौघात्","m":"cluster of gems"},{"d":"देवराज्यात्","m":"Lord of gods"},{"d":"विशिष्यते","m":"higher"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"अर्थतश्चमयाप्राप्तादेवरज्यादयोगुणाः हतशत्रुंविजयिनंरामंपश्यामिसुस्थितम् ।","trans":"\"Now that the enemy is killed, Rama is happy, which means as if I have attained the rulership of gods.\"","words":[{"d":"हतशत्रुम्","m":"enemy killed"},{"d":"विजयिनम्","m":"victorious"},{"d":"सुस्थितम्","m":"happy"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"पश्यामि","m":"see"},{"d":"अर्थतः","m":"meaningful"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"देवराज्यादयः","m":"rulership of gods"},{"d":"गुणाः","m":"virtues"},{"d":"प्राप्ताः","m":"attained"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"तस्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वामैथिलीजनकात्मजा ततःशुभतरंवाक्यमुवाचपवनात्मजम् ।","trans":"Hearing the words of Mythili, daughter of Janaka, Hanuman spoke these auspicious words.","words":[{"d":"जनकात्मजा","m":"Janaka's daughter"},{"d":"मैथिली","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"her"},{"d":"तत्","m":"those"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"ततः","m":"that"},{"d":"पवनात्मजम्","m":"son of wind god"}